quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  74,18,"Lalle ne, Shi, yã yi tunãni, kuma yã ƙaddara (abin da zai faɗã game da Alƙur'ãni)"
  74,19,"Sabõda haka, aka la'ane shi, kamar yadda ya ƙaddara"
  74,20,"Sa'an nan, aka la'ane shi kamar yadda ya ƙaddara"
  74,21,"Sa'an nan, ya yi tunãni"
  74,22,"Sa'an nan, ya gintse huska? kuma ya yi murtuk"
  74,23,"Sa'an nan, ya jũya bãya, kuma ya bunƙãsa"
  74,24,"Sai ya ce: \"Wannan abu dai bã kõme ba ne fãce wani sihiri, wanda aka ruwaito"
  74,25,Wannan maganar mutum dai ce
  74,26,Zã Ni ƙõna shi da Saƙar
  74,27,Kuma mẽ ya sanar da kai abin da akẽ cẽwa Saƙar
  74,28,"Bã ta ragẽwa, kuma bã ta bari"
  74,29,Mai nãcẽwa ga jiki ce (da (ƙũna)
  74,30,A kanta akwai (matsara) gõma shã tara
  74,31,"Kuma ba Mu sanya ma'abũta wutã (wãto matsaranta) ba, fãce malã'iku, kuma ba Mu sanya adadinsu (gõma sha tara) ba, fãce dõmin fitina ga waɗanda suka kãfirta domin waɗanda aka bai wa littãfi su sãmi yaƙĩni kuma waɗanda suka yi ĩmãni su ƙãra ĩmãni, kuma waɗanda aka bai wa littãfi da mũminai bã zã su yi shakka ba, kuma domin wa ɗanda a cikin zukatansu akwai wata cuta da kãfirai su ce: \"Mẽ Allah Yake nufi da wannan, ya kasance misãli?\" Haka dai Allah ke ɓatar da wanda Ya so, kuma Ya shiryar da wanda ya so. Kuma bãbu wanda ya san mayãƙan Ubangijinka fãce Shi, kuma ita (wutar) ba ta kasance ba fãce wata tunãtarwa ce ga mutum"
  74,32,A'aha! Ina rantsuwa da watã
  74,33,Da dare a lõkacin da ya jũyar da baya
  74,34,Da sãfiya idan ta wãye
  74,35,Ita (wutar) ɗayan manyan masĩfũ? ce
  74,36,Mai gargaɗĩ ce ga mutum
  74,37,"Ga wanda ya so, daga cikinku, ya gabãta ko ya jinkirta"
  74,38,Kõwane rai ga abin da ya aikata jingina ce
  74,39,Fãce mutãnen dãma
  74,40,A cikin Aljanna suna tambayar jũna
  74,41,Game da mãsu laifi
  74,42,"(Su ce musu) \"Me ya shigar da ku a cikin Saƙar"
  74,43,"Suka ce: \"Ba mu kasance munã a cikin mãsu salla ba"
  74,44,Kuma ba mu kasance muna ciyar da matalautã ba
  74,45,Kuma mun kasance muna kũtsãwa tãre da mãsu kũtsãwa
  74,46,Mun kasance munã ƙaryata rãnar sãkamako
  74,47,Har gaskiya (wãto mutuwa) ta zo mana